                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D816870" rel="nofollow">Freddy123</a> 的线索投递！</div>
            <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 12 月 6 日消息，苹果今日向 Apple Watch 用户推送了 watchOS 10.2 更新（内部版本号：21S364），本次更新距离上次发布隔了 27 天。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="苹果 watchOS 操作系统" height="461" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2022/4/8bd386fb-ecc7-474d-bd95-4c69ba122e7a.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzEzOC5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_14,x_14,a_0/format,f_auto" title="苹果 watchOS 10.2 候选版发布：Siri 可访问和记录 Health 数据" width="900" /></p><p>需要注意的是，因苹果各区域节点服务器配置缓存问题，可能有些地方探测到升级更新的时间略有延迟，一般半小时内，不会太久。</p><p>IT之家附上 watchOS 10.2 候选版本更新内容如下：</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>使用&nbsp; Siri 访问和记录 Health 应用数据</p></li><li><p>在靠近 HomePod Mini 或者第二代 HomePod 之后，如果正在播放来自 Music 或者播客的内容，自动切换到 Now Playing 视图。</p></li><li><p>在设置中启用滑动更换表盘功能</p></li><li><p>在“设置”中启用确认结束体能训练的功能</p></li><li><p>在大多数 Fitness+ 体能训练中，优先考虑音乐或教练声音的音量</p></li><li><p>修复了可能导致在 <a class="s_tag" href="https://iphone.ithome.com/" target="_blank">iPhone</a> 上的 Watch App 中添加表盘后，无法在 Apple Watch 上显示的问题</p></li></ul><h3>附 watchOS 10 发布历史：</h3><ul class="custom_reference  ai-word-checked list-paddingleft-1"><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/735/703.htm" target="_blank">2023-11-29：watchOS 10.2 Beta 4 (21S5358a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/732/576.htm" target="_blank">2023-11-15：watchOS 10.2 Beta 3 (21S5349e)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/731/426.htm" target="_blank">2023-11-10：watchOS 10.2 Beta 2 (21S5342e)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/730/806.htm" target="_blank">2023-11-08：watchOS 10.1.1 (21S71)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/727/950.htm" target="_blank">2023-10-27：watchOS 10.2 Beta (21S6331f)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/725/620.htm" target="_blank">2023-10-11：watchOS 10.1 Release Candidate (21S67)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/724/056.htm" target="_blank">2023-10-11：watchOS 10.1 Beta 3 (21S5063a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/722/968.htm" target="_blank">2023-10-04：watchOS 10.1 Beta 2 (21S5053f)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/722/168.htm" target="_blank">2023-09-28：watchOS 10.1 Beta (21S5042f)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/721/890.htm" target="_blank">2023-09-27：watchOS 10.0.2 (21R371)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/720/836.htm" target="_blank">2023-09-22：watchOS 10.0.1 (21R360)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/718/720.htm" target="_blank">2023-09-13：watchOS 10 Release Candidate (21R356)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/715/662.htm" target="_blank">2023-08-30：watchOS 10 Beta 8 (21R5355a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/714/157.htm" target="_blank">2023-08-23：watchOS 10 Beta 7 (21R5349b)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/712/621.htm" target="_blank">2023-08-16：watchOS 10 Beta 6 (21R5341c)</a></p></li